1. Explain about main method and  Why main() method is public, static and void in java ?

-> main() method is a starting point of execution of a java program. JVM will call the main() method.
   public static void main(String[] args){}  ,String[] args is array of object we need to pass that object from the 
   command line.
   every Java program have at list one main() method.
   
   
   
   
   
